ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87dfcce9eb8d537b691fff3b376a5d58595d654f","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"快啲啦<br />\n五毛想出名wor"},{"pid":"6e256eb15eea1d98a71ee3590770b1fac7731c16","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"係咪唔幫五毛先<br />\n五毛一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8f1130c4e9cac79b0971dba1f8e0aae5644e9e","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"五毛 出黎啦<br />\n召喚白金級五毛"},{"pid":"196b90aadf6c31980c95431118bb4082ea83f525","tid":1553582,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"[建議] 出黎發夢或者遊行，我都會同朋友講....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553546</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acb37b831cb73aeb78a176c0562a22c1dcecfc91","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"我地係幾個讀緊社會大學幾年既90後，其實我地係睇左《前線就黎餓死喇》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510171</a> 呢個post而決定組織呢個計劃，我地留左tg，發現真係有為數不少既小朋友因爲做左發夢王而同屋企人鬧交/無飯食/荷包乾塘，我地好心痛大家捱住麵包發夢，所以希望呢個計劃可以幫到一班小朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單講下個開飯計劃：<br />\n<br />\n1. 希望大家可以捐飯券/現金券比我地，不收現金！不收現金！不收現金！<br />\n2. 我地會因應飯券數量而決定援助範圍，希望優先幫到所有tg我地既小朋友先，如果飯券數量充裕，我地係會上前線派比小朋友！<br />\n3. 為保障安全，小朋友領取飯券係不需要露面！不需要親身交收！<br />\n<br />\n以下開放Q&amp;A，自答幾題先<br />\n如果有意見，歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ.點解要信你？<br />\nA.我只會答，香港人而加呢個時候只能講個信字，我都係寧願去信會搵我既小朋友係真係需要幫助而去幫佢，我只能發誓，所有券都會用黎俾出去發夢既小朋友，我地唔會中飽私囊。<br />\n<br />\nQ.小朋友幾耐可以申請一次？<br />\nA.一個星期一次，每晚9點截止，會預1-2天處理好申請同發放飯券。<br />\n<br />\nQ.會收啲咩物資？<br />\nA.只收飯券/現金券！唔收錢！唔收八達通！<br />\n<br />\n總之，歡迎大家俾任何食得飽既飯券我地，餅券就最好唔好啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ.大人想俾飯券你地可以點交收？<br />\nA.我地會安排義工係地鐵沿線同大家交收，唔同站請pm番唔同既義工，但我地人手有限，希望大家體諒我地未必覆蓋到所有站。<br />\n<br />\nChannel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/freedomofsummer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreedomofsummer&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=a0d92b3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freedomofsummer</a><br />\n<br />\n求下仔女們真係唔好怕醜，食飽先有力氣繼續行落去，歡迎大家搵我地呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你地每一位既幫忙，香港人真係好有愛，香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d9976499e9b4aa8a29d2ed580484669c2921f","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"快啦 幫五毛出名"},{"pid":"cc296749b5c6a4ab2779e0dca48bee82a76cdd2d","tid":1553582,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲豬呀？</span>"},{"pid":"1d9f9f309e63183582a4c22e3b63be72d453c0e9","tid":1553582,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe39d7ad5af140c7f79c5d30e84b136fd4b3987","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc296749b5c6a4ab2779e0dca48bee82a76cdd2d","tid":1553582,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲豬呀？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔係 你想出名阿嘛<br />\n五毛"},{"pid":"68ef091eb508a093ee001e708c0d0e81d938ebc6","tid":1553582,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc296749b5c6a4ab2779e0dca48bee82a76cdd2d","tid":1553582,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲豬呀？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:55:48.000Z","msg":"宜家幫你搞大佢"}]}